                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/28537739/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2013-09-11 22:28
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="14263948">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/DylenNewman/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1860328-24.jpg" alt="Dylen" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/14263948/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/14263948/" class="">第39页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/DylenNewman/" class=" " title="Dylen">Dylen</a>
                (是个病人家属)
              
                <span class="allstar30" title="还行"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="14263948">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">而所谓现代性的悲剧，正在于人类所产生的客体剥夺了人类自身的生命。它们就像齐美尔笔下的形式，对人类产生规定作用，但事实上，人类本应该去规定它们。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-08-25 11:47</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>而所谓现代性的悲剧，正在于人类所产生的客体剥夺了人类自身的生命。它们就像齐美尔笔下的形式，对人类产生规定作用，但事实上，人类本应该去规定它们。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
